s</a> logo), and Combination Marks (e.g., <a href="https://www.logoshape.com/mcdonalds-vector-logo-1991.html">McDonald&#8217;s</a>). Some sources also include categories such as Letterforms, Monograms, and Dynamic Logos.</p><div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-984b5853 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:40px;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;font-size:16px"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-cbc690f8 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><a href="https://www.logoshape.com/square-logos"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.logoshape.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/square-logos.svg" alt="square logos" class="wp-image-655" style="width:62px"/></a></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:24px"><a href="https://www.logoshape.com/square-logos">Square Logos</a></h3><p class="has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;font-size:16px"><a href="https://www.logoshape.com/square-logos">Provide a stable and balanced appearance.</a></p></div><div class="wp-block-column has-ast-global-color-5-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained"><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-medium is-resized"><a href="https://www.logoshape.com/circle-logos"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.logoshape.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/circle-logos-1.svg" alt="circle logos" class="wp-image-654" style="width:62px"/></a></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:24px"><a href="https://www.logoshape.com/circle-logos">Circle Logos</a></h3><p class="has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset